1
00:00:21,120 --> 00:00:22,160
You're finally back.

2
00:00:23,440 --> 00:00:24,480
I've long awaited you.

3
00:00:25,199 --> 00:00:26,440
If I weren't a loyal man,

4
00:00:26,440 --> 00:00:27,199
I'd have left already.

5
00:00:29,079 --> 00:00:30,359
Close the door.

6
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:44,320
Look at your smug face.

7
00:00:44,320 --> 00:00:45,479
Did you find anything out?

8
00:00:45,479 --> 00:00:46,479
Nothing.

9
00:00:46,719 --> 00:00:48,439
I didn't find too many clues.

10
00:00:48,439 --> 00:00:49,840
You know I'm a modest person.

11
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:53,359
According to the grain and pattern
of the wood,

12
00:00:53,359 --> 00:00:55,520
after a series of calculations,

13
00:00:55,520 --> 00:00:56,359
I can confirm

14
00:00:56,719 --> 00:00:58,640
that the box set should have four parts.

15
00:00:59,399 --> 00:01:02,600
And these two just happen
to be the first and the last.

16
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,840
I've mentioned this material before.

17
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:04,920
It's not considered very good.

18
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:06,359
However, what surprises me

19
00:01:06,359 --> 00:01:07,400
is the era.

20
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:09,439
It likely dates to the Kangxi era.

21
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:11,560
Although it's not exactly ancient,

22
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:13,319
it's still a century-old item,

23
00:01:13,319 --> 00:01:14,599
which is somewhat interesting.

24
00:01:14,599 --> 00:01:15,280
The craftsmanship

25
00:01:15,959 --> 00:01:16,599
is not bad,

26
00:01:17,040 --> 00:01:18,816
but it can't compare to that
of a master.

27
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:20,840
It's probably the wood carving
from the Quanzhou area.

28
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:22,239
Even if there's something special,

29
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,760
it's impossible to find out who made it.

30
00:01:25,319 --> 00:01:26,799
Even if the person were confirmed,

31
00:01:27,599 --> 00:01:29,239
he'd certainly be long dead by now.

32
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:30,319
Just tell me

33
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:32,319
what exactly is so special about it.

34
00:01:33,439 --> 00:01:34,120
Special.

35
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:36,040
Indeed there is something special.

36
00:01:36,079 --> 00:01:37,120
Only a genius like me

37
00:01:37,359 --> 00:01:39,159
can discover

38
00:01:39,159 --> 00:01:40,079
something special about it.

39
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:44,439
It is the lacquer.

40
00:01:44,439 --> 00:01:45,120
The lacquer?

41
00:01:45,312 --> 00:01:45,879
Yes.

42
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:47,319
These two charred pieces of wood

43
00:01:47,319 --> 00:01:48,480
seems to have been painted twice.

44
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,680
And obviously it was painted again

45
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,120
for the second time,

46
00:01:51,599 --> 00:01:53,799
which was almost

47
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:54,920
decades after the first time.

48
00:01:55,719 --> 00:01:57,040
So, this second coat of lacquer

49
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,680
must be done to cover up something.

50
00:01:59,120 --> 00:01:59,879
What is it?

51
00:02:00,519 --> 00:02:01,359
I don't know yet.

52
00:02:01,359 --> 00:02:02,799
We'll see after we remove the lacquer.

53
00:02:03,799 --> 00:02:05,159
I am a person of manners.

54
00:02:05,159 --> 00:02:06,319
Without your permission,

55
00:02:06,319 --> 00:02:07,719
I dare not damage your things.

56
00:02:08,719 --> 00:02:09,280
Mr. Lin,

57
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:10,360
go head.

58
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:10,960
Alright.

59
00:02:45,199 --> 00:02:45,960
Five.

60
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,599
Bao.

61
00:02:52,639 --> 00:02:53,719
What is this?

62
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:01,639
Muqing,

63
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:03,960
let's be frank since we're on one side.

64
00:03:04,639 --> 00:03:05,400
This thing

65
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,680
is related to the Altar Treasure, right?

66
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:10,840
Otherwise, you wouldn't offer
a price of one thousand taels.

67
00:03:12,879 --> 00:03:13,919
For the sake of brotherhood,

68
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:14,879
I don't want

69
00:03:14,879 --> 00:03:15,599
one thousand taels.

70
00:03:16,439 --> 00:03:18,240
When you go searching
for the secret treasure,

71
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,319
please ensure I'm included.

72
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,439
You know me well.

73
00:03:22,199 --> 00:03:23,479
Firstly, I have a discerning eye.

74
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:24,639
I can recognize all treasures.

75
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:25,360
Secondly,

76
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:28,120
including piecing together
the porcelain jar in Shanxi,

77
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,719
I've already helped you twice.

78
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:30,719
Furthermore,

79
00:03:30,759 --> 00:03:32,400
without my discovery

80
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,479
of the second layer of paint,

81
00:03:34,479 --> 00:03:35,080
Muqing,

82
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,199
these characters
would have remained unseen.

83
00:03:38,199 --> 00:03:39,639
Although these few words

84
00:03:39,639 --> 00:03:41,280
are kind of baffling,

85
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,800
if you take me along,

86
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,520
I'm sure I can be of help.

87
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,680
Isn't it always me

88
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:48,479
who unravels the key information?

89
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,680
As long as you agree to take me along,

90
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:52,560
I will surely do my utmost

91
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:54,680
to trace the origin of the set
of charred wooden box.

92
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,080
Then you must...

93
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:58,840
Keep it a secret.

94
00:03:59,039 --> 00:04:00,120
It must be kept confidential.

95
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:02,759
I won't tell a word of it to others.

96
00:04:02,759 --> 00:04:03,479
Muqing,

97
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:05,280
you can trust me.

98
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:07,120
Getting rich quietly,

99
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:09,159
that's my good nature.

100
00:04:23,759 --> 00:04:25,199
Four sealed parts.

101
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:29,800
I choose a simple and peaceful life

102
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:33,319
over official strife,
despite being laughed.

103
00:04:33,399 --> 00:04:34,399
That is to say to Prince Qi

104
00:04:34,399 --> 00:04:36,160
also has no chance to get it.

105
00:04:36,839 --> 00:04:38,759
That's actually good news.

106
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:39,639
Sir,

107
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:42,399
I think it is not the time to give up.

108
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,120
Do you think there's still a chance?

109
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,519
Although Zhuo Bufan

110
00:04:45,519 --> 00:04:46,879
possesses one of the four seals,

111
00:04:47,439 --> 00:04:49,560
he may not necessarily win against us.

112
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:50,839
That's true.

113
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:53,240
But at least you get one first,

114
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,800
so that the Department

115
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,560
can be invincible.

116
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:57,759
Although now

117
00:04:58,279 --> 00:05:00,319
the remaining seals' clues are unclear,

118
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:03,199
the information we've obtained

119
00:05:03,199 --> 00:05:04,439
is much more than before.

120
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,560
I've had a feeling

121
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:07,600
that many clues have already been found.

122
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,759
Once we decipher one or two,

123
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:10,040
we can unravel the mystery.

124
00:05:11,319 --> 00:05:14,000
As you're confident, I'll be at ease.

125
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:16,000
Sir, I have promised to try my best,

126
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:18,600
so it is far from admitting defeat now.

127
00:06:06,336 --> 00:06:11,008
=Heroes=

128
00:06:12,544 --> 00:06:14,272
=Episode 23=

129
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,460
(24th day of the fourth month, 1911)

130
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:19,392
(Grain in Ear is 16 days away)

131
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,600
You want to join me in
finding the Altar Treasure?

132
00:06:27,839 --> 00:06:28,480
Yes.

133
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:31,079
Haven't we already cooperated?

134
00:06:32,199 --> 00:06:34,680
We tracked Zhuo Bufan together before.

135
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,879
Now, it's treasure hunting.

136
00:06:35,879 --> 00:06:36,839
Indeed different.

137
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:40,120
So this time you come to me

138
00:06:40,879 --> 00:06:43,480
as a soldier of Beiyang or...

139
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,720
The treasure belongs to the court

140
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:47,279
no matter whether I'm second lieutenant
of the 43rd Association

141
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:49,000
or a constable at the Dagu County Yamen.

142
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:49,759
It's all the same.

143
00:06:52,199 --> 00:06:53,480
I've never doubted

144
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,839
your loyalty to the court.

145
00:06:54,959 --> 00:06:55,759
Mr. Muqing,

146
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,839
for our cooperation this time,

147
00:06:57,839 --> 00:07:00,160
I hope we can be open and honest.

148
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,560
It seems you're quite confident.

149
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,680
Where have you been these days?

150
00:07:06,879 --> 00:07:08,800
Zhuo Bufan found a clue

151
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,759
and went to Tianjin.

152
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,439
Therefore I followed him

153
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,319
only to find his target is the inheritor

154
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:18,120
of the chief of Dharma Department.

155
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,000
Did he find the man?

156
00:07:19,199 --> 00:07:19,879
Yes.

157
00:07:20,639 --> 00:07:22,360
Is the man dead?

158
00:07:23,519 --> 00:07:24,879
Zhuo Bufan killed him.

159
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:27,160
Did Zhuo Bufan get anything?

160
00:07:28,199 --> 00:07:30,079
He did not get the Dharma Seal.

161
00:07:30,079 --> 00:07:31,279
But you got it?

162
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:33,040
So I hope this collaboration can

163
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,000
be open and honest.

164
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,040
Good.

165
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,680
Be open and honest.

166
00:07:44,079 --> 00:07:46,040
I remember you once said,

167
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,360
to open the Altar Treasure,

168
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,120
two treasure maps are required.

169
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:51,199
Now it seems that we may need three.

170
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:52,240
That was the past.

171
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,600
Now I can be sure

172
00:07:53,879 --> 00:07:55,040
that a total of four are needed.

173
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,639
Four?

174
00:07:56,879 --> 00:07:58,959
Zhuo Bufan has the Discipline Seal,

175
00:07:58,959 --> 00:08:00,120
and you said

176
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:02,319
he almost got the Seal
of Dharma Department,

177
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,360
which ended up with you.

178
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:05,079
That's good.

179
00:08:05,759 --> 00:08:07,480
You know about
the Seal of Bodhi Department.

180
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:08,360
Yes.

181
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,879
It was you who entered Futu Temple.

182
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:12,920
So we're still one short.

183
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:15,879
No clues at all?

184
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,079
No clues at all.

185
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:23,519
Well,

186
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:27,079
what does your seal look like?

187
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,240
It's the same as yours.

188
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:33,879
How about showing it to me first?

189
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:36,360
Let me have a look first.

190
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,360
What's this?

191
00:08:55,799 --> 00:08:56,480
This is...

192
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,679
Don't you know it?

193
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,600
It's the box for the seal.

194
00:09:09,039 --> 00:09:09,568
Right.

195
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,440
You haven't seen it before?

196
00:09:14,399 --> 00:09:15,399
I...

197
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:16,840
Right,

198
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:19,480
not all seals are placed in boxes.

199
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:20,879
Exactly.

200
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:24,720
The shorter one is the seal of
Disciplinary Department,

201
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,799
which is obtained
from the palace by Zhuo Bufan.

202
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:28,080
The longer one is the Bodhi Seal.

203
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,960
What does the characters on this mean?

204
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,240
I don't know.

205
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,759
They are intermittent.

206
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:42,440
I pondered for days
yet remained puzzled.

207
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,639
I'm still expecting

208
00:09:43,639 --> 00:09:45,519
you could bring a section of the box

209
00:09:45,519 --> 00:09:46,799
to gather a few more characters.

210
00:09:47,159 --> 00:09:47,840
I know.

211
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,320
Really?

212
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:52,279
Bao refers to Baohe Inn.

213
00:09:52,279 --> 00:09:54,879
Five, the sixth day of the fifth month.
Three, the thirty-year appointment.

214
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,440
Baohe Inn.

215
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,519
The sixth day of the fifth month.
The thirty-year appointment.

216
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:02,799
When do these thirty years count from?

217
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:05,200
I don't know it.

218
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:08,000
However, for the precise time of
the thirty-year appointment,

219
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:08,919
I do know.

220
00:10:10,679 --> 00:10:11,559
It's the year of Xinhai

221
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:13,240
that is this year.

222
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:14,720
How did you come to know this?

223
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,200
Before the passing of Dharma's chief,

224
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:18,799
these words were left behind.

225
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,799
Since they're on the sealed box,

226
00:10:24,799 --> 00:10:27,360
and also spoken by
the inheritor of Southern Shaolin,

227
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:32,240
this must be
the appointed time and place

228
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,039
for all the inheritors to meet.

229
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:37,639
If this appointment occurs once
every thirty years,

230
00:10:37,639 --> 00:10:39,960
then counting back thirty years
from the year of Xinhai,

231
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,360
it would be

232
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,840
1881.

233
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:45,200
Pushing back another thirty years
would be 1851.

234
00:10:45,639 --> 00:10:48,399
Another thirty back would be 1821.

235
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:51,039
Then comes 1791.

236
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:52,600
1761.

237
00:10:52,919 --> 00:10:53,799
And finally...

238
00:10:55,639 --> 00:10:56,279
Which year?

239
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:58,320
1701,

240
00:10:58,639 --> 00:11:00,799
which is when the court sent troops
to wipe out Southern Shaolin.

241
00:11:00,799 --> 00:11:02,720
It's the year
when even the temple was burnt down.

242
00:11:04,039 --> 00:11:05,480
Your analysis is right.

243
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,600
The year of Xinhai

244
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:08,039
marks another thirty-year appointment.

245
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,720
The sixth day of the fifth month

246
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:11,559
should be the specific time to meet.

247
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:12,639
On this day,

248
00:11:12,639 --> 00:11:14,759
all four inheritors of
Southern Shaolin should appear.

249
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:17,519
The inheritor of
the Bodhi Department won't show up.

250
00:11:17,519 --> 00:11:18,879
However, I can pretend to be him

251
00:11:18,879 --> 00:11:20,639
to attend this thirty-year appointment.

252
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:23,080
The inheritor of Dharma is already dead.

253
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,440
But you obtain the seal,

254
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:26,559
you are qualified to go with me.

255
00:11:27,519 --> 00:11:29,919
The Disciplinary Department's inheritor
has aligned with the court,

256
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:31,440
so I suppose he would not appear.

257
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:33,720
However, Zhuo Bufan holding its seal,

258
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,840
will surely be able to make it.

259
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:37,320
So that leaves one person remaining.

260
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:40,440
Someone we know nothing about.

261
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,080
The fourth seal.

262
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,559
The fourth seal.

263
00:11:45,519 --> 00:11:47,960
Perhaps on that day,

264
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,000
all will be answered.

265
00:11:52,519 --> 00:11:53,840
Where is Baohe Inn?

266
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:58,559
I sought you believing you'd know.

267
00:11:58,559 --> 00:11:59,960
How would I know?

268
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:01,320
You are from the Department

269
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,279
and a master detective.

270
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,919
Can't you find out by investigating?

271
00:12:04,039 --> 00:12:05,440
I've already told you the name.

272
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,440
You're sure to find it.

273
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,840
Alright.

274
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,919
I'll look into it.

275
00:12:08,919 --> 00:12:09,720
Me too.

276
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:10,360
Mr. Muqing,

277
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,879
once we find any information,

278
00:12:12,879 --> 00:12:14,200
let's immediately share it.

279
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,039
Alright.

280
00:12:15,039 --> 00:12:16,360
Let's be frank and open.

281
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,279
Frank and open.

282
00:12:25,519 --> 00:12:27,000
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

