374
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:19,759
This is Miss Liu,
my classmate from my studies abroad.

375
00:16:21,279 --> 00:16:22,279
This is my husband.

376
00:16:22,759 --> 00:16:23,879
Hello, Miss Liu.

377
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:24,879
I'm Zhong Haichao.

378
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,080
Hello, Mr. Zhong.

379
00:16:26,840 --> 00:16:28,600
