380
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:30,559
Haichao is a Beiyang commander.

381
00:16:31,879 --> 00:16:33,000
You're indeed striking.

382
00:16:34,519 --> 00:16:36,039
I won't keep you from your classmate.

383
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:39,320
Please sit.

384
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:43,639
