00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:12,359
a very generous gift.

561
00:25:12,359 --> 00:25:14,240
I hope you can present it
to His Highness.

562
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:15,960
If His Highness accepts it,

563
00:25:15,960 --> 00:25:18,839
then I could be
at ease, reassured, and content.

564
00:25:20,079 --> 00:25:22,640
Ordinary items naturally won't suffice.

565
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:24,559
But this is extraordinary.

566
00:25:24,559 --> 00:25:26,279
It's a famed master's carving
from Shoushan stone.

567
00:25:26,279 --> 00:25:28,400
It's at least three hundred years old.

568
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:30,240
And it comes from no ordinary origin.

569
00:25:41,119 --> 00:25:42,119
Who is it exactly?

570
00:25:42,319 --> 00:25:44,359
It's a Southeast Asian merchant
dealing with antiques.

571
00:25:44,559 --> 00:25:46,160
It's all jewelry and stuff like that.

572
00:25:46,319 --> 00:25:47,920
The princess invited you to take a look.

573
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:49,160
Thank the princess.

574
00:25:49,160 --> 00:25:50,359
They are indeed quite beautiful.

575
00:25:50,440 --> 00:25:52,279
Lucky always brings
something interesting.

576
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:53,440
Who?

577
00:25:53,960 --> 00:25:55,000
His name is Lin Haohan.

578
00:25:55,200 --> 00:25:56,599
He comes from Southeast Asia,

579
00:25:57,119 --> 00:25:58,400
so he insists on being called Lucky.

580
00:25:59,960 --> 00:26:01,160
Oh my.

581
00:26:01,599 --> 00:26:02,680
My stomach is hurting again.

582
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:04,759
Tell the princess I can't come over.

583
00:26:06,319 --> 00:26:07,519
I just need to rest a bit.

584
00:26:13,640 --> 00:26:14,680
What is this?

585
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:16,079
It's for you.

586
00:26:18,240 --> 00:26:19,079
From you?

587
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:20,960
A merchant.

588
00:26:21,160 --> 00:26:22,160
He recently opened a shop,

589
00:26:22,160 --> 00:26:23,680
a large antique and curio store,

590
00:26:23,839 --> 00:26:25,079
which is just around Qianmen.

591
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:27,960
This is specifically for you, Father.

592
00:26:30,079 --> 00:26:31,480
A merchant?

593
00:26:32,079 --> 00:26:33,759
What good stuff can a merchant offer?

594
00:26:34,519 --> 00:26:35,440
Put it away.

595
00:26:35,720 --> 00:26:36,640
Father,

596
00:26:36,640 --> 00:26:38,160
at least take a look.

597
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:39,759
He also said

598
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:41,920
this is a famed Shoushan stone carving

599
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:43,160
over three hundred years,

600
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:45,240
and its provenance is extraordinary.

601
00:26:45,720 --> 00:26:48,920
It is said to be
a Buddhist artifact from Fujian,

602
00:26:48,920 --> 00:26:51,000
a paperweight of
the former Southern Shaolin Abbot.

603
00:26:52,839 --> 00:26:53,920
What is it called?

604
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:56,519
Lotus Step.

605
00:26:57,200 --> 00:26:58,240
Lotus Step?

606
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:01,000
Prince Qi's Mansion?

607
00:27:01,279 --> 00:27:03,880
To be precise, Wulan Shan's place.

608
00:27:04,759 --> 00:27:06,519
Men Sandao actually took Liu Lin

609
00:27:06,519 --> 00:27:07,960
to the home of princess.

610
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:10,640
Is the Department cooperating

611
00:27:10,640 --> 00:27:12,160
with Prince Qi or Beiyang?

612
00:27:12,160 --> 00:27:15,240
Men Sandao never mentioned it
to Wang Jialuo.

613
00:27:15,440 --> 00:27:17,920
He didn't even mention

614
00:27:17,920 --> 00:27:19,119
Liu Lin at all.

615
00:27:19,400 --> 00:27:21,039
I asked the servants in the mansion,

616
00:27:21,559 --> 00:27:24,119
they said Liu Lin was a classmate
of Wulan Shan during studying abroad,

617
00:27:24,640 --> 00:27:26,599
who came back from abroad to visit her.

618
00:27:27,240 --> 00:27:29,599
Wulan Shan told Zhong Haichao the same.

619
00:27:32,680 --> 00:27:34,319
Zhong Haichao was unaware.

620
00:27:34,880 --> 00:27:36,759
According to what I've gotten,

621
00:27:37,480 --> 00:27:38,759
he was truly unaware.

622
00:27:39,759 --> 00:27:40,960
So it was Wulan Shan

623
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:43,000
who fabricated an identity for Liu Lin.

624
00:27:43,279 --> 00:27:43,920
Yes.

625
00:27:46,519 --> 00:27:49,480
I didn't know Men Sandao and Wulan Shan

626
00:27:49,759 --> 00:27:51,079
have such a close relationship.

627
00:27:52,880 --> 00:27:54,359
At first, I was also puzzled.

628
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:56,240
So, I looked into it.

629
00:27:57,079 --> 00:27:59,319
I had someone inquire
in the Imperial Household Department.

630
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:00,920
Twelve years ago,

631
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:03,440
Guangxu once wanted to act
as the matchmaker

632
00:28:03,720 --> 00:28:06,160
and have Welan Shan marry Men Sandao.

633
00:28:06,279 --> 00:28:07,319
Twelve years ago?

634
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:08,480
The year of the Wuxu Reform.

635
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:11,400
After the reform,
Men Sandao was prisoned.

636
00:28:12,079 --> 00:28:13,079
If it hadn't been for this,

637
00:28:13,559 --> 00:28:15,640
he would have been
the prince's son-in-law.

638
00:28:16,799 --> 00:28:19,559
So, they had affection
for each other at that time.

639
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:22,359
Does Zhong Haichao know it?

640
00:28:22,720 --> 00:28:24,160
It shouldn't be a secret anymore.

641
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:25,960
It's just that no one mentions it.

642
00:28:27,000 --> 00:28:29,079
It was for paving the way for his career

643
00:28:29,680 --> 00:28:31,079
that Zhong Haichao married the princess.

644
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:34,839
Men Sandao used the relationship

645
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:36,480
to hide Liu Lin in Wulan Shan's mansion.

646
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:38,680
He was quite clever.

647
00:28:39,359 --> 00:28:41,079
I feel it's rather simple instead.

648
00:28:42,599 --> 00:28:44,480
There are imperial guards
and Beiyang guards

649
00:28:44,839 --> 00:28:45,960
in Wulan Shan's mansion,

650
00:28:46,640 --> 00:28:48,240
but they will not necessarily
be on high alert.

651
00:28:48,279 --> 00:28:49,640
After all, it is a prince's home.

652
00:28:49,640 --> 00:28:51,079
Presumably those guards

653
00:28:51,079 --> 00:28:52,960
have long been accustomed to peace.

654
00:28:53,920 --> 00:28:56,440
Men Sandao won't
expose Liu Lin's identity,

655
00:28:56,759 --> 00:28:59,880
while Wulan Shan will
only admit Liu Lin is her classmate.

656
00:29:00,119 --> 00:29:02,119
Thus, defense won't be
intentionally bolstered.

657
00:29:03,519 --> 00:29:06,400
Perhaps we should go to
her mansion to abduct Liu Lin.

658
00:29:06,559 --> 00:29:09,559
It might be easier than
going to Men Sandao's home.

659
00:29:11,240 --> 00:29:11,759
Okay.

660
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,160
Get ready.

661
00:29:13,480 --> 00:29:14,400
Act as soon as possible.

662
00:29:14,559 --> 00:29:16,519
Find some martial artists this time.

663
00:29:16,839 --> 00:29:18,240
Be sure not to expose yourself.

664
00:29:21,359 --> 00:29:23,200
You just maintain your current state.

665
00:29:33,119 --> 00:29:33,759
Huanjie.

666
00:29:33,920 --> 00:29:34,519
Bufan.

667
00:29:35,519 --> 00:29:38,440
Are you going to report to Prince Qi?

668
00:29:38,640 --> 00:29:39,240
Yes.

669
00:29:39,759 --> 00:29:41,160
Without any results,

670
00:29:41,519 --> 00:29:42,759
we can't escape a scolding for sure.

671
00:29:43,279 --> 00:29:44,279
But it'll be okay.

672
00:29:46,720 --> 00:29:47,480
Well, Huanjie.

673
00:29:48,799 --> 00:29:49,880
This time it'll be a rebuke,

674
00:29:50,480 --> 00:29:51,640
so I'll go alone

675
00:29:52,000 --> 00:29:52,960
without you.

676
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:55,960
That's good.

677
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:57,119
However, Bufan,

678
00:29:57,799 --> 00:29:58,799
you must remember

679
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:00,119
to bear with it.

680
00:30:01,079 --> 00:30:02,680
Don't make the prince angry.

681
00:30:07,559 --> 00:30:08,359
I know.

682
00:30:18,279 --> 00:30:21,079
But he has been waiting for a long time.

683
00:30:21,559 --> 00:30:22,480
Let him wait.

684
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:23,279
Alright.

685
00:30:23,519 --> 00:30:24,960
No need to serve tea.

686
00:30:25,720 --> 00:30:26,279
Yes.

687
00:30:33,519 --> 00:30:34,240
Mr. Zhuo,

688
00:30:36,440 --> 00:30:37,799
the prince wants you to wait.

689
00:30:40,440 --> 00:30:41,519
He is busy with official duties.

690
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:45,359
I shall wait then.

691
00:30:52,440 --> 00:30:53,119
Mr. Muqing,

692
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:54,400
I received a tip

693
00:30:55,119 --> 00:30:57,359
that someone had gathered
a dozen scattered forces

694
00:30:57,680 --> 00:30:58,519
to act tonight.

695
00:30:58,960 --> 00:30:59,920
How does that concern us?

696
00:31:01,000 --> 00:31:02,920
It's said the organizer is a woman.

697
00:31:03,160 --> 00:31:04,799
Well, isn't it either a man or a woman?

698
00:31:07,839 --> 00:31:09,000
That Japanese woman?

699
00:31:09,079 --> 00:31:09,920
Nobody has seen her.

700
00:31:09,920 --> 00:31:10,640
It can't be sure.

701
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:12,559
However, they did kidnap someone before.

702
00:31:13,200 --> 00:31:14,160
I fear just in case...

703
00:31:14,680 --> 00:31:15,799
It seems they've already known

704
00:31:15,799 --> 00:31:17,200
I've placed Miss Liu
in the prince's place.

705
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:20,400
They are quite bold,

706
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:22,039
daring to take actions there.

707
00:31:23,119 --> 00:31:24,079
Let's go, Getai.

708
00:31:24,079 --> 00:31:26,000
Change clothes and take a walk there.

709
00:31:34,440 --> 00:31:35,599
Go ahead and have a look.

710
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:38,119
Excuse me.

711
00:31:40,359 --> 00:31:41,480
Sugar-coated haws.

712
00:31:41,480 --> 00:31:44,279
Sugar-coated haws.

713
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:49,279
All sorts here.

714
00:31:49,279 --> 00:31:50,519
Come and see.

715
00:31:50,519 --> 00:31:52,200
Sugar-coated haws.

716
00:31:55,039 --> 00:31:55,839
Sesame cake.

717
00:31:56,119 --> 00:31:58,000
A bowl of plain noodles, please.

718
00:31:58,119 --> 00:31:59,119
Sesame cake.

719
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:00,240
Come on.

720
00:32:06,599 --> 00:32:07,440
Two bowls please.

721
00:32:07,759 --> 00:32:08,359
Alright.

722
00:32:11,039 --> 00:32:12,640
This place was a good choice.

723
00:32:12,640 --> 00:32:14,799
If it were me, I would choose here too.

724
00:32:15,079 --> 00:32:17,440
The southwest corner of the mansion
is the back kitchen

725
00:32:17,440 --> 00:32:18,920
with fewer guards.
Easier to cause chaos.

726
00:32:19,519 --> 00:32:20,319
It's out-of-the-way.

727
00:32:20,319 --> 00:32:22,160
When it gets dark,
there will be even fewer people.

728
00:32:23,039 --> 00:32:23,880
A good choice.

729
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:26,359
I've spotted the forces as well.

730
00:32:26,759 --> 00:32:27,720
Seventeen, right?

731
00:32:33,119 --> 00:32:34,119
Counted already?

732
00:32:36,400 --> 00:32:37,640
Muqing, don't say it just yet.

733
00:32:37,640 --> 00:32:38,519
Let me have a try.

734
00:32:40,559 --> 00:32:42,279
Those five over there pulling the cart.

735
00:32:42,279 --> 00:32:43,400
It's almost dark.

736
00:32:43,880 --> 00:32:45,720
Who would need
cart pullers at this time?

737
00:32:46,319 --> 00:32:47,920
They're for the getaway.

738
00:32:48,359 --> 00:32:50,720
Tie up Miss Liu
and carry her away on the cart.

739
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:52,079
It's too slow using a cart.

740
00:32:52,079 --> 00:32:53,880
After the abduction,
there should be a car.

741
00:32:54,200 --> 00:32:56,119
The cart is loaded
with weapons and ropes.

742
00:32:56,400 --> 00:32:57,720
The wall-scaling abduction

743
00:32:57,720 --> 00:32:59,240
can't do without these tools.

744
00:33:00,079 --> 00:33:00,920
You're right.

745
00:33:01,839 --> 00:33:03,599
Those two playing chess under
the tree to the west

746
00:33:03,960 --> 00:33:04,839
are surrounded by five.

747
00:33:04,839 --> 00:33:05,880
Seven in total.

748
00:33:06,440 --> 00:33:08,000
We don't know whether it's good or not.

749
00:33:08,759 --> 00:33:10,839
One of the onlookers
is carrying a lantern.

750
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:15,839
Has he figured it out

751
00:33:15,839 --> 00:33:17,680
that the game would last until dark?

752
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:19,400
You have a keen eye.

753
00:33:20,039 --> 00:33:21,880
I learn from the best.

754
00:33:23,079 --> 00:33:23,960
It seems

755
00:33:23,960 --> 00:33:25,000
my boys and I

756
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:27,079
also did a poor job back then.

757
00:33:28,720 --> 00:33:30,640
And there, the one peeling radishes.

758
00:33:31,599 --> 00:33:34,880
The radishes are almost
the size of carrots now.

759
00:33:35,039 --> 00:33:36,400
Will anyone buy these?

760
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:37,960
There must be something off.

761
00:33:38,119 --> 00:33:39,599
And the one over there with the hook.

762
00:33:41,920 --> 00:33:43,640
As if he fears others won't know
what he does.

763
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:47,160
And those two at the noodle shop.

764
00:33:48,359 --> 00:33:49,519
How long have they been eating?

765
00:33:49,720 --> 00:33:50,680
The noodles must be mushy.

766
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:56,240
You said seventeen.

767
00:33:56,440 --> 00:33:57,279
Where's the last one?

768
00:34:06,920 --> 00:34:08,400
Your noodle tea is good.

769
00:34:10,719 --> 00:34:12,960
Is it millet flour or sorghum flour?

770
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:15,480
It's millet flour.

771
00:34:16,119 --> 00:34:16,840
Getai.

772
00:34:17,039 --> 00:34:18,800
Don't you think the millet mush
is very good?

773
00:34:18,800 --> 00:34:20,039
Yes, it's authentic.

774
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:22,239
But he doesn't even know

775
00:34:22,239 --> 00:34:23,800
what flour this is made of.

776
00:34:28,559 --> 00:34:29,760
It's dark under the lamp.

777
00:34:31,400 --> 00:34:33,199
I actually overlooked you.

778
00:34:34,079 --> 00:34:35,039
A hefty investment.

779
00:34:35,039 --> 00:34:36,280
They're from Zhao's store,

780
00:34:36,639 --> 00:34:37,960
where the price is not cheap.

781
00:34:38,159 --> 00:34:40,559
You must have spent much buying these.

782
00:34:41,800 --> 00:34:43,719
We don't have to buy them today, do we?

783
00:34:43,960 --> 00:34:44,960
Of course not.

784
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:46,199
Take this back and the boys can have

785
00:34:46,199 --> 00:34:47,239
a bowl of authentic millet mush

786
00:34:47,239 --> 00:34:49,639
if they are tired from interrogation.

787
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:52,960
You guys will act tonight, right?

788
00:34:53,159 --> 00:34:53,800
Well,

789
00:34:53,920 --> 00:34:55,440
why did you come so early?

790
00:34:55,519 --> 00:34:57,079
You don't need to scout the place.

791
00:34:57,760 --> 00:34:59,239
Let's take you all back.

792
00:35:00,599 --> 00:35:02,760
Will you be tough to deal with?

793
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:04,639
It won't matter in that case.

794
00:35:04,880 --> 00:35:06,079
There are still sixteen left.

795
00:35:06,440 --> 00:35:07,960
There's always someone who'll cave.

796
00:35:08,199 --> 00:35:08,960
Don't be still.

797
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:10,679
We still want two more bowls.

798
00:35:10,800 --> 00:35:11,559
Come on.

799
00:35:13,159 --> 00:35:13,880
They act now?

800
00:35:15,519 --> 00:35:16,039
Go.

801
00:35:24,719 --> 00:35:26,559
You all came back yesterday.

802
00:35:27,719 --> 00:35:31,400
Why do you report back today?

803
00:35:33,719 --> 00:35:38,000
Did you achieve nothing
in Tianjin Presidio?

804
00:35:38,639 --> 00:35:39,960
Do you feel you've let me down?

805
00:35:41,039 --> 00:35:42,480
The disciples and I

806
00:35:42,480 --> 00:35:44,440
indeed found that madman
outside of Tianjin yesterday.

807
00:35:44,639 --> 00:35:45,840
We also confirmed

808
00:35:45,840 --> 00:35:47,920
he is the fourth-generation chief
of Dharma Department.

809
00:35:48,559 --> 00:35:49,880
But he has been insane for forty years.

810
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:51,039
We couldn't get anything from him.

811
00:35:51,360 --> 00:35:53,280
We could not find any clues either

812
00:35:53,280 --> 00:35:54,760
in his residence or on his body.

813
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:57,639
I have spared no effort.

814
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:59,639
So it's not a matter of
letting you down.

815
00:36:01,480 --> 00:36:03,079
You've thought for a whole day

816
00:36:03,440 --> 00:36:06,320
and concluded
that you haven't let me down?

817
00:36:07,119 --> 00:36:08,039
Then tell me,

818
00:36:08,559 --> 00:36:09,960
after thinking for a whole day,

819
00:36:09,960 --> 00:36:12,320
what is the next step in your plan?

820
00:36:13,480 --> 00:36:14,639
I haven't thought of it yet.

821
00:36:18,159 --> 00:36:20,480
What's Baohe Inn?

822
00:36:22,440 --> 00:36:23,480
Baohe Inn?

823
00:36:23,679 --> 00:36:24,840
You've thought for a whole day

824
00:36:24,840 --> 00:36:27,119
but haven't figured out the next step.

825
00:36:27,599 --> 00:36:29,960
But Men Sandao
in the Imperial Household Department

826
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:31,719
has stirred things up all day.

827
00:36:31,880 --> 00:36:33,119
What has he discovered?

828
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:36,199
I don't know.

829
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:37,599
But someone came to report

830
00:36:37,840 --> 00:36:40,960
that he has ordered
a search through historical records.

831
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:44,400
He has gone back two hundred years,

832
00:36:45,119 --> 00:36:48,480
looking for a place called Baohe Inn.

833
00:36:48,840 --> 00:36:51,239
